## Steps to setup mysql db for Icinga Web2

# https://wiki.icinga.org/display/howtos/Setting+up+Icinga+with+IDOUtils+on+RHEL

$ psql template1
psql>  create database <%= @db_name -%>;

$ createlang plpgsql <%= @db_name -%>

psql> create role <%= @db_user -%>;

psql> alter role <%= @db_user -%> login;

psql> grant all on database <%= @db_name -%> to <%= @db_user -%>;

$ psql -U <%= @db_user -%> -d <%= @db_name -%> < <%= @schema_file -%>
